# QA Report — Sprint M4a
Round: 1

Spec reviewed: `tasks/spec.md` (M4a — Instagram Slide-1 Cover-Centering + Image-Grid-Cap)
Codebase read: `slide-template.tsx`, `instagram-post.ts`, `instagram-overrides.ts`, `instagram-layout/route.ts`, `instagram/route.ts`, `memory/lessons.md`, patterns `nextjs-og.md`, `react.md`.

